ComicInfo.Title: House Call; Art Class; Window Peeker; Old Walt; $!
ComicInfo.Summary:
The hiring of a stripper for a figure drawing class doesn't work out as planned.
Dennis recalls a childhood friend's eccentric neighbor.
Denny and friends visit a house of ill repute.
